</para><simplesectsep/><para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>XST_SUCCESS if all operations complete successfully.</para></listitem><listitem><para>XST_FAILURE if any operation fails.</para></listitem></itemizedlist>
</para><simplesectsep/><para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>XST_SUCCESS, if example is run successfully.</para></listitem><listitem><para>XST_FAILURE, in case of failure. </para></listitem></itemizedlist>
</para></simplesect>
</para>        </detaileddescription>
